      "content": "\"soul awareness\"? idk that sounds a bit too hippy-dippy for what i'm feeling. it felt much more physical than that, like a literal discord in the sound waves. like the pitch was slightly \"off\" in a way that made my teeth ache. is there a more... scientific way to look at it? like, could there be an actual pattern in the audio frequency that changes when someone is being dishonest?",
